### Zaloguj się jako admin i zapisz token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "resource",
  "password": "password"
}

### Pobierz wszystkie zasoby (getAllResources)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/resources

### Pobierz zasób po ID (getResourceById)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/resources/60c72b2f9b1e8a3f3c8e4b2a

### Utwórz nową książkę (createResource - Book)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/resources
Authorization: Bearer {{resource_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "book",
  "name": "Morderstwo w Orient Expressie2",
  "description": "Herkules Poirot po rozwiązaniu sprawy kryminalnej w Azji wraca do Europy.",
  "author": "Agatha Christie",
  "isbn": "9788327159779"
}

### Utwórz nowe czasopismo (createResource - Periodical)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/resources
Authorization: Bearer {{resource_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "periodical",
  "name": "CD-Action",
  "description": "Magazyn o grach komputerowych",
  "issueNumber": 320
}

### Utwórz nową gazetę (createResource - Newspaper)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/resources
Authorization: Bearer {{resource_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "newspaper",
  "name": "Gazeta Wyborcza",
  "description": "Gazeta",
  "releaseDate": "15-11-2025"
}

### Edytuj zasób (editResource)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/resources/60c72b2f9b1e8a3f3c8e4b2d
Authorization: Bearer {{resource_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "releaseDate": "15-11-2026"
}

### Usuń zasób po ID (deleteResource) #wpisz-id
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/resources/----
Authorization: Bearer {{resource_token}}
